// Tutorial 8 — Polymetry
//
// {voice1, voice2} plays voices simultaneously.
// Both voices are stretched to the same total duration.
// So 3 notes against 4 notes creates a polymetric rhythm.
//
// Try: add a third voice with 5 notes.

